beer.beer_description:
This American Sour has been kettle soured and is bursting with zesty aromas and flavours. Showcasing a juicy mouthfeel with a balanced tart finish, it is the perfect refresher on a warm Summers day. It offers the richness of Spring with the bounty of Summer!

Brewed in collaboration with Beer Cartel, Australia's leading independent craft beer store.
